ZH: 他是一个很厚道的人，总是乐于助人。
EN: He is a very honest person, always willing to help others.

ZH: 这家餐厅的老板非常厚道，经常给员工加工资。
EN: The owner of this restaurant is very generous, often giving raises to the employees.

